---
import '@fontsource/inter/400.css';
import '@fontsource/inter/500.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/400.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/500.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/600.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/700.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Legal Notice — Oyparaploo</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0px, #ffffff 300px, #fdfcfb 700px, #f9f7f4 100%);
    color: #2a2320;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 100px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 425;
    color: #5a4f47;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: #5a4f47;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #3d352e;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #2a2320;
    margin-top: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  a {
    color: #2a2320;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: #b8a088;
  }
  a:hover { text-decoration-color: #2a2320; }

  .address-block {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .copyright-line {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
  }

  .colophon {
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1.2px solid #777;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #7d7168;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .content { padding: 40px 20px 60px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="content">

  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">&#8249; Back</a></div>

  <h1>Legal Notice</h1>

  <p>Oyparaploo is a multidisciplinary practice located in Saint Paul and Minneapolis, Minnesota. This site <a href="https://oyparaploo.com">oyparaploo.com</a> is the place where Oyparaploo's online archive resides.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>

  <div class="address-block">
    Brian Otto<br>
    Oyparaploo<br>
    Saint Paul<br>
    <a href="mailto:info@oyparaploo.com">info@oyparaploo.com</a>
  </div>

  <h2>Copyright</h2>

  <p class="copyright-line">&copy; 2026 Brian Otto / Oyparaploo. All rights reserved.</p>

  <h2>Disclosed Outside Resources</h2>

  <p>References and links to works by other artists, writers, and musicians. This is an interpretive language and application of concepts, beliefs, and methods. Including: writing, found text, voice transcription, characters, documentary narrative, fiction, and mixed voice projects.</p>

  <p>If something presented on this website concerns you, please send a message to ~ <a href="mailto:info@oyparaploo.com">info@oyparaploo.com</a>.</p>

  <div class="colophon">
    Oyparaploo · Minneapolis ~ Saint Paul<br>
    Wonderful Garbage · Noir Chanson
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>